																		Just wondering...
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser deleted" data-id="2306764"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/common--images/avatars/default/a16.png" alt=""/>(account deleted)</span> <span class="odate time_1448715411 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">28 Nov 2015 12:56</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2414470">
									

<p>Is SCP-3125 the &quot;contagious murder&quot; from <a href="/we-need-to-talk-about-fifty-five">We Need to Talk About Fifty-Five</a> or is it some unrelated SCP that hasn't been mentioned before?</p>

							</div>

										<div class="signature">
					<hr class="signature-separator"/>
					

<p><em>Yea, though I walk through the lowest rated pages, I will fear no coldpost: for thou art with me SCP Wiki; thy mods and thy staff they comfort me.</em>- Proxymoron</p>

				</div>
					
					
